-- China Resources Gas Group Plans to Triple Projects, Morning Post Reports
-- B y   D e b r a   M a o
-- 2010-09-26T23:53:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-26/china-resources-gas-group-plans-to-triple-projects-morning-post-reports.html
China Resources Gas Group plans to
almost triple its number of projects in three years at a cost of
10 billion yuan, the South China Morning Post reported, Chief
Financial Officer Ken Ong Thiam Kin.  Ong said the company aims to increase its number of
projects from 32 to 90 by 2013, raising its total annual gas
sales to 9 billion cubic metres, the newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
